<a href="?PHPSESSID=6dae4ae03df45fddc8e4a0a03b23caaa&amp;action=profile;u=6105" title="检视会员资料:  聪明伶俐琪露诺">聪明伶俐琪露诺</a>
</h4>
<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_1121042_extra_info">
<li class="title">侵略！バガ娘！<li class="postgroup">Goddess<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="avatar" style="overflow: auto;">
