[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1121357'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1121357'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #6 于:</strong> 2021-07-01, 周四 22:29:41 &#187;</div>
