<h4>
<img src="Themes/celeste/images/useroff.gif" alt="离线"/>
<a href="?PHPSESSID=6dae4ae03df45fddc8e4a0a03b23caaa&amp;action=profile;u=6105" title="检视会员资料:  聪明伶俐琪露诺">聪明伶俐琪露诺</a>
</h4>
